 skin diseases; see Lv 13–14"}]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Luk:17:13","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"and raised their voices, saying, “Jesus, Master, "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Lk 5:5","book":"Luk","chapter":5,"verse":5,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"text","text":" have mercy on us!”"}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Lk 5:5","book":"Luk","chapter":5,"verse":5}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Luk:17:14","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"When he saw them, he told them, “Go and show yourselves to the priests.”"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Lv 13:2","book":"Lev","chapter":13,"verse":2,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Mt 8:4","book":"Mat","chapter":8,"verse":4,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Lk 5:14","book":"Luk","chapter":5,"verse":14,"letter":"c"},{"kind":"text","text":" And while they were going, they were cleansed."}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Lv 13:2","book":"Lev","chapter":13,"verse":2},{"label":"Mt 8:4","book":"Mat","chapter":8,"verse":4},{"label":"Lk 5:14","book":"Luk","chapter":5,"verse":14}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Luk:17:15","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"But one of them, seeing that he was healed, returned and, with a loud voice, gave glory to God. "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Mt 9:8","book":"Mat","chapter":9,"verse":8,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Mk 2:12","book":"Mrk","chapter":2,"verse":12,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Lk 2:14","book":"Luk","chapter":2,"verse":14,"letter":"c"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Lk 5:26","book":"Luk","chapter":5,"verse":26,"letter":"d"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Jn 9:24","book":"Jhn","chapter":9,"verse":24,"letter":"e"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ac 4:21","book":"Act","chapter":4,"verse":21,"letter":"f"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ac 12:23","book":"Act","chapter":12,"verse":23,"letter":"g"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Rm 4:20","book":"Rom","chapter":4,"verse":20,"letter":"h"},{"kind":"text","text":" "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Mt 9:8","book":"Mat","cha