"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Gn 6:14","book":"Gen","chapter":6,"verse":14,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"text","text":" and the flood came and destroyed them all. "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Lk 20:34–35","book":"Luk","chapter":20,"verse":34},{"label":"Gn 6:14","book":"Gen","chapter":6,"verse":14}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Luk:17:28","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"It will be the same as it was in the days of Lot:"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Gn 19:1–26","book":"Gen","chapter":19,"verse":1,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"text","text":" People went on eating, drinking, buying, selling, planting, building. "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Gn 19:1–26","book":"Gen","chapter":19,"verse":1}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Luk:17:29","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"But on the day Lot left Sodom, fire and sulfur rained from heaven and destroyed"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Gn 19:24–25","book":"Gen","chapter":19,"verse":24,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"text","text":" them all. "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Gn 19:24–25","book":"Gen","chapter":19,"verse":24}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Luk:17:30","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"It"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Mt 24:17","book":"Mat","chapter":24,"verse":17,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Mt 24:39","book":"Mat","chapter":24,"verse":39,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Mk 13:15","book":"Mrk","chapter":13,"verse":15,"letter":"c"},{"kind":"text","text":" will be like that on the day the Son of Man is revealed."},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Mt 16:27","book":"Mat","chapter":16,"verse":27,"letter":"d"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Mt 24:44","book":"Mat","chapter":24,"verse":44,"letter":"e"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"1Co 1:7","book":"1Co","chapter":1,"verse":7,"letter":"f"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"2Th 1:7","book":"2Th","chapter":1,"verse":7,"letter":"g"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"1Pt 1:7","book":"1Pe","chapter":1,"verse":7,"letter":"h"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"1Pt 4:13","book"